// An entry self-loop with an orphan self-loop node that's unreachable from the entry. Both
// {0} and {1} are terminal SCCs of the original CFG, so `add_infinite_loop_post_dominators`
// adds an impossible edge to each. Structuring's DFS post-order starts from node 0 and never
// visits node 1, so the unreachable orphan is silently dropped and the output is just the
// entry's loop.
//
//   ->0     ->1
//    \_|     \_|

code,0,0
code,1,1
